high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove.
Look up and take the bowl out of the microwave.
Turn right and veer right to the fridge.
Place the bowl in the fridge on the shelf under the lettuce. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn left and walk to the counter with the coffee maker.
Place the bowl on the counter to the left of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated bowl on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and move forward, then turn left to go toward the stove; look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave, take the bowl from inside, then close the microwave.
Turn around and go across the room, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the bowl inside and chill it, then take the bowl out.
Turn left and go to the counter across the room.
Place the bowl on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl on the counter.

high_descs: Make a right to walk to the microwave.
Take out a black cup from the microwave.
Turn around and hang a left to get to the fridge.
Chill the black cup in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn around to walk to the countertop to the right of the stove.
Set the black cup down on the countertop to the right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Chill a black cup from the microwave to put on the countertop next to the stove.
